<% if @bulk_order%>
  Hello from C360,

  You have a Bulk order for <%=@bulk_order.order_item.name%>.

  The order in total was for <%=@bulk_order.max_amount%> grams
  Total Price: <%=@bulk_order.max_amount * @item.price%>

  <%@bulk_order.user_orders.each do |user_order|%>
    <%= user_order.user.email%> in <%= user_order.user.city%>,<%= user_order.user.state%>.
    They bought <%= user_order.quantity%> for $<%=user_order.quantity * @item.price%>.
